{"id":48,"ayahs":[{"number":282,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓا۟ إِذَا تَدَايَنتُم بِدَيْنٍ إِلَىٰٓ أَجَلٍۢ مُّسَمًّۭى فَٱكْتُبُوهُ ۚ وَلْيَكْتُب بَّيْنَكُمْ كَاتِبٌۢ بِٱلْعَدْلِ ۚ وَلَا يَأْبَ كَاتِبٌ أَن يَكْتُبَ كَمَا عَلَّمَهُ ٱللَّهُ ۚ فَلْيَكْتُبْ وَلْيُمْلِلِ ٱلَّذِى عَلَيْهِ ٱلْحَقُّ وَلْيَتَّقِ ٱللَّهَ رَبَّهُۥ وَلَا يَبْخَسْ مِنْهُ شَيْـًۭٔا ۚ فَإِن كَانَ ٱلَّذِى عَلَيْهِ ٱلْحَقُّ سَفِيهًا أَوْ ضَعِيفًا أَوْ لَا يَسْتَطِيعُ أَن يُمِلَّ هُوَ فَلْيُمْلِلْ وَلِيُّهُۥ بِٱلْعَدْلِ ۚ وَٱسْتَشْهِدُوا۟ شَهِيدَيْنِ مِن رِّجَالِكُمْ ۖ فَإِن لَّمْ يَكُونَا رَجُلَيْنِ فَرَجُلٌۭ وَٱمْرَأَتَانِ مِمَّن تَرْضَوْنَ مِنَ ٱلشُّهَدَآءِ أَن تَضِلَّ إِحْدَىٰهُمَا فَتُذَكِّرَ إِحْدَىٰهُمَا ٱلْأُخْرَىٰ ۚ وَلَا يَأْبَ ٱلشُّهَدَآءُ إِذَا مَا دُعُوا۟ ۚ وَلَا تَسْـَٔمُوٓا۟ أَن تَكْتُبُوهُ صَغِيرًا أَوْ كَبِيرًا إِلَىٰٓ أَجَلِهِۦ ۚ ذَٰلِكُمْ أَقْسَطُ عِندَ ٱللَّهِ وَأَقْوَمُ لِلشَّهَٰدَةِ وَأَدْنَىٰٓ أَلَّا تَرْتَابُوٓا۟ ۖ إِلَّآ أَن تَكُونَ تِجَٰرَةً حَاضِرَةًۭ تُدِيرُونَهَا بَيْنَكُمْ فَلَيْسَ عَلَيْكُمْ جُنَاحٌ أَلَّا تَكْتُبُوهَا ۗ وَأَشْهِدُوٓا۟ إِذَا تَبَايَعْتُمْ ۚ وَلَا يُضَآرَّ كَاتِبٌۭ وَلَا شَهِيدٌۭ ۚ وَإِن تَفْعَلُوا۟ فَإِنَّهُۥ فُسُوقٌۢ بِكُمْ ۗ وَٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ ۖ وَيُعَلِّمُكُمُ ٱللَّهُ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ بِكُلِّ شَىْءٍ عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"O YOU who have attained to faith! Whenever you give or take credit for a stated term, set it down in writing. And let a scribe write it down equitably between you; and no scribe shall refuse to write as God has taught him: thus shall he write. And let him who contracts the debt dictate; and let him be conscious of God, his Sustainer, and not weaken anything of his undertaking. And if he who contracts the debt is weak of mind or body, or, is not able to dictate himself, then let him who watches over his interests dictate equitably. And call upon two of your men to act as witnesses; and if two men are not available, then a man and two women from among such as are acceptable to you as witnesses, so that if one of them should make a mistake, the other could remind her. And the witnesses must not refuse [to give evidence] whenever they are called upon. And be not loath to write down every contractual provision, be it small or great, together with the time at which it falls due; this is more equitable in the sight of God, more reliable as evidence, and more likely to prevent you from having doubts [later]. If, however, [the transaction] concerns ready merchandise which you transfer directly unto one another, you will incur no sin if you do not write it down. And have witnesses whenever you trade with one another, but neither scribe nor witness must suffer harm; for if you do [them harm], behold, it will be sinful conduct on your part. And remain conscious of God, since it is God who teaches you [herewith] - and God has full knowledge of everything.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/289.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":87945,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87946,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87947,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوٓا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87948,"position":4,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87949,"position":5,"arabic":"تَدَايَنتُم","translation":"তোমরা পরস্পরে আদান-প্রদান কর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87950,"position":6,"arabic":"بِدَيْنٍ","translation":"ঋণের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87951,"position":7,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","translation":"পর্যন্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87952,"position":8,"arabic":"أَجَلٍۢ","translation":"মেয়াদ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87953,"position":9,"arabic":"مُّسَمًّۭى","translation":"নির্দিষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87954,"position":10,"arabic":"فَٱكْتُبُوهُ ۚ","translation":"তা তোমরা তখন লিখে রাখো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87956,"position":11,"arabic":"وَلْيَكْتُب","translation":"এবং যেন লেখে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87957,"position":12,"arabic":"بَّيْنَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87958,"position":13,"arabic":"كَاتِبٌۢ","translation":"একজন লেখক","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87959,"position":14,"arabic":"بِٱلْعَدْلِ ۚ","translation":"ন্যায্যভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87961,"position":15,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87962,"position":16,"arabic":"يَأْبَ","translation":"অস্বীকার করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87963,"position":17,"arabic":"كَاتِبٌ","translation":"কোনো লেখক","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87964,"position":18,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে (না)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87965,"position":19,"arabic":"يَكْتُبَ","translation":"সে লিখবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87966,"position":20,"arabic":"كَمَا","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87967,"position":21,"arabic":"عَلَّمَهُ","translation":"শিখিয়েছেন তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87968,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87970,"position":23,"arabic":"فَلْيَكْتُبْ","translation":"অতএব সে যেন লেখে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_282_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87971,"position":24,"arabic":"وَلْيُمْلِلِ","translation":"এবং যেন সে লিখিয়ে নেয় (লেখ্য বিষয়